column5: Good morning Guys!!!!!  Need some help here!  Is there any good fishing around Frankford, just north of Trenton on the trib of Trent?  Please let me know.  Looking to play a bit of hookie tomorrow from work since the weather seems alright.  Probably my last trip of 2006 and then truly hanging it up until April for springtime crappies!  Thanks in advance!
PM me for some details I know a few spots on there that you can catch pretty much what ever you want
